com.josip.personal.address.book.controllers

Class TemplateController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.josip.personal.address.book.controllers.TemplateController

  • @Controller
public class TemplateController
extends java.lang.Object
    Since:
    24.5.2019 14:10
    Version:
    1.0

    Description

    This class receive request and send requests. Data is sent to user view by repository. First, list is generated and repository is used to receive data from database. Then, lambda expression is used to add data to the list. List is added to the model then, which controller will pass to the web site. User will see that data at the site.
